metadata.description: Soulware is a generative NFT collection anchored in the Ethereum blockchain as snapshot of inner child. The fight between Unirare and the Soulwarriors has begun and the supply will be determined by the community. The story begins with the Soulware: Origins, the Genesis [collection](https://opensea.io/collection/soulware-origins) Soulware will be providing breeding, Sandbox integration, clothing brands partnerships and special IRL events. Welcome to the Soulware Project.
metadata.name: Soulware #1
